data.description: An exciting opportunity for investment or primary residence in a prime north end location. This charming single-level home sits on low-traffic street close to schools, parks and library which is attractive to potential tenants and owners alike! Spacious home with newer HVAC, windows and flooring in 2020. The fully fenced east facing backyard has raised garden beds, updated and well manicured landscaping.
